org.openimaj.image.processing.morphology

Class StructuringElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.morphology.StructuringElement

  • public class StructuringElement
extends Object
    Morphological structuring element The central element is the pixel 0,0. Other s.e. pixels are relative to this.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
